- âŒ `FiBug` - DOES NOT EXIST - Use `FiAlertCircle` instead
- âŒ `FiCube` - DOES NOT EXIST - Use `FiBox` instead
- âŒ `FiLightbulb` - DOES NOT EXIST - Use `FiZap` instead
- âŒ `FiTag` - For categories, use `FiBookmark` instead

