## ğŸ§ª TESTING CHECKLIST - RUN THIS BEFORE EVERY PUSH

```bash
# 1. Check for absolute imports
grep -r "from '@/components" app/ && echo "âŒ FOUND ABSOLUTE IMPORTS" || echo "âœ… No absolute imports"

# 2. Check for invalid icons
grep -r "FiPalette\|FiBug\|FiCube\|FiLightbulb" app/ && echo "âŒ FOUND INVALID ICONS" || echo "âœ… No invalid icons"

# 3. Check for custom hex codes
grep -r "#[0-9A-Fa-f]\{6\}" app/ --include="*.tsx" --include="*.ts" | grep -v "475569\|64748b\|94a3b8\|ffb7c5\|c5e6ff\|d2b7ff\|b7ffca" && echo "âŒ FOUND CUSTOM COLORS" || echo "âœ… Only palette colors"

# 4. Check for 'use client'
grep -L "use client" app/dashboard/**/page.tsx && echo "âŒ PAGES MISSING 'use client'" || echo "âœ… All pages have 'use client'"

# 5. Check ITEMS_PER_PAGE
grep -r "ITEMS_PER_PAGE =" app/ | grep -v "6" && echo "âŒ NON-STANDARD PAGINATION" || echo "âœ… Pagination is 6"
```

